Package com.teksystems.salestaxexercise.runners

Classes used to run end-to-end tests of the entire module. And also data that is useful for unit tests across the module.
Author:
Andrew
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SalesTaxExerciseRunner
    Contains the static SalesTaxExerciseRunner.main(String[]) function used to run and test the entire project.
    TestHelpers
    Constructs objects that simplify testing this module.
    TestHelpers.Baskets
    Pre-built test Baskets (all Canadian right now).
    TestHelpers.Goods
    Basic Good objects corresponding to the goods used in this exercise.
    TestHelpers.Goods.AmericanGoods
    Good objects with the USA as their region of origin.
    TestHelpers.Goods.CanadianGoods
    Good objects with Canada as their region of origin.
    TestHelpers.Goods.FrenchGoods
    Good objects with France as their region of origin.
    TestHelpers.PricedGoods
    PricedGood objects corresponding to the prices for the goods used in this exercise.
    TestHelpers.PricedGoods.CanadianPrices
    The PricedGood list for Canada.
    TestHelpers.PricedGoods.CanadianPrices.CanadianImportPrices
    The PricedGoods for Canada that are imports.
